      "rationale": "Model inputs factor scoped to not-assessed at MRL 2 per credibility plan CP-CPB-2024-01. Nominal input values drawn from published FDA benchmark dataset. Sensitivity of NIH to ±5% variation in viscosity and density confirmed negligible in preliminary scoping analysis, supporting the not-assessed designation."
